  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7733408">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7733408/" class="title-link">晚明南方聪明人的选择</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7733408"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2749285/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2749285-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2749285/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">spinachs</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-01-13"
      class="main-meta">2016-01-13 06:57:54</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7733408_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在特定的大时代背景下个人无法把控外部世界，退而求其次，经营自己的小世界，聪明人把种种享受也发挥到极致，感官被磨砺得极纤维敏锐。在灰暗的背景色努力经营一小块绚丽的色彩。慢慢细读真是享受。也许是最近这种形势更能理解那时那人。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
